==军事用途==
烏戈爾尼機場是[[苏联空军|苏联空军]]远程航空兵的九个北极前进跳板机场（bounce aerodrome）之一，可用于远程战略轰炸机返程时降落加油维修。<ref name="sal80">[https://www.cia.gov/library/readingroom/docs/CIA-RDP80T01355A000100140001-2.pdf STRATEGIC ARMS LIMITATIONS RELATED ACTIVITIES SUMMARY REPORT (SANITIZED)] {{Wayback|url=https://www.cia.gov/library/readingroom/docs/CIA-RDP80T01355A000100140001-2.pdf |date=20190125020338 }}, June 1, 1980, CREST: CIA-RDP80T01355A000100140001-2, Central Intelligence Agency, Washington, DC.</ref> 

烏戈爾尼機場是[[苏联国土防空军|苏联国土防空军]]的重要空军基地，一个{{tsl|en|Yakovlev Yak-28|雅克-28}}截击机(Firebar)团与[[S-75导弹|S-75]]地对空导弹，用于拦截阿拉斯加[[美国空军|美国空军]]的抵近侦察飞行，并对部署在[[阿纳德尔|阿纳德尔]]东北13km处打击阿拉斯加的战略预警目标的[[R-12德维纳河导弹|R-12]]中程液体弹道核导弹阵地提供保护。<ref name="missile65">Evaluations of Soviet Surface-to-Surface Missile Deployment, November 1965, Guided Missile and Astronautics Intelligence Committee, Central Intelligence Agency, Washington, DC.</ref> 1982年9月，一个[[Su-15攔截機|Su-15攔截機]]团取代了{{tsl|en|Yakovlev Yak-28|雅克-28}}。<ref>[https://www.cia.gov/library/readingroom/document/cia-rdp83t00574r000101020001-2 FLAGON DEPLOYMENT ANADYR/UGOLNYYE KOPI AIRFIELD, USSR (SANITIZED)] {{Wayback|url=https://www.cia.gov/library/readingroom/document/cia-rdp83t00574r000101020001-2 |date=20190612093828 }}, September 27, 1982, CIA-RDP83T00574R000101020001-2, Central Intelligence Agency, Washington, DC.</ref>其番号是{{tsl|en|11th Air Army|防空第11集团军}}防空第23军歼击航空兵第171团，从[[阿布哈兹|阿布哈兹]]的[[古達烏塔|古達烏塔]]调防。 <ref name="#1"/> 1992年，烏戈爾尼機場的航空兵撤销。

2001年的一次训练飞行中，[[Tu-95轟炸機|图-95]]MS战略轰炸机与[[伊尔-78|伊尔-78]]加油机从{{tsl|en|Engels-2 (air base)|恩格斯空军基地}}飞来。

2014年，俄官方宣布计划在烏戈爾尼機場部署[[米格-31戰鬥機|Mig-31]]截击机。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://theaviationist.com/2014/10/28/mig-31-based-arctic/ |title=存档副本 |access-date=2019-03-06 |archive-date=2020-12-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201201134332/https://theaviationist.com/2014/10/28/mig-31-based-arctic/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

